问题一：Code signing “AipBase.framework” failed.

解决：

步骤1：在xcode中找到包含x86_64, i386的framework。如图所示序号4这里面的3个framework里面(AipBase.framewok,IdcardQuality.framework,AipOcrSdk.framework)都包含着x86_64, i386。

步骤2：用script命令去掉这3个framework里面不支持的x86_64, i386的结构

问题二：更新了mac系统,想pod install 报错:zsh: /usr/local/bin/pod: bad interpreter: /System/Library/Frameworks/Ruby.framework

解决:终端输入：sudo gem install -n /usr/local/bin cocoapods
